well this particular 'bug' is more of a visual one<br />the item is selected, its just not the active selection. this can be reproduced with a mouse by opening 2 windows, selecting something in 1 window, then clicking the other window..<br />the item in the origional window is still selected, its just not active and selected... (in windows XP i believe; it used to be a dotted line around the file, but in windows 7, its just a less-visible version of fully selected.<br />If your looking to change it, its likely part of the theme file... but it wont be easy... <img src="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/images/smilies/icon_razz.gif" alt=":P" title="Razz" /><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=62">Jcee</a> — Mon Mar 25, 2013 6:11 pm</p><hr />
